      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/ge-healthcare-misses-quarterly-revenue-estimates-weakness-china-market-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国市场销量下降以及扫描设备需求弱于预期的影响，GE医疗科技周二第一季度营收未达到预期，导致其股价盘前暴跌12%。]]></description>
